es/low-grade-heat-from-renewable-sources-could-be-used-to-desalinate-water.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 15 Nov 2025 10:11:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/11/low-grade-heat-from-renewable-sources-could-be-used-to-desalinate-water</guid></item></channel></rss>